\v 7 \x * \xo 24:7 \xt Lu 9:22, 17:25\x*вАШHi M…®t…®k ke wit ke M…®t…®k Iuwe, m…®t han nanwisa hi eno his me m…®t enun nises menmen enum te h…®r nanwenk…®ka hahu nu tentarak…®t hi hahi. Te maain hi p…®ke ah…®krit ehu are m…®t…®k me w…® wikak.вАЩвАЭ   
